'''海上核材料运输民事责任公约'''（{{Lang-en|Convention relating to Civil Liability in the Field of Maritime Carriage of Nuclear Material}}）是1971年[[國際海事組織|国际海事组织]]（时称政府间海事咨询组织）制订的[[国际公约|国际公约]]。公约于[[比利时|比利时]][[布鲁塞尔|布鲁塞尔]]通过，于1975年7月15日生效，保存人是国际海事组织秘书长。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Convention relating to Civil Liability in the Field of Maritime Carriage of Nuclear Material (NUCLEAR)|url=https://www.imo.org/en/About/Conventions/Pages/Convention-relating-to-Civil-Liability-in-the-Field-of-Maritime-Carriage-of-Nuclear-Material-(NUCLEAR).aspx|accessdate=2021-02-09|publisher=www.imo.org|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210704155215/https://www.imo.org/en/About/Conventions/Pages/Convention-relating-to-Civil-Liability-in-the-Field-of-Maritime-Carriage-of-Nuclear-Material-(NUCLEAR).aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Convention relating to civil liability in the field of maritime carriage of nuclear material (with Final Act and official Russian and Spanish translations )|url=https://treaties.un.org/pages/showDetails.aspx?objid=0800000280107d4b|accessdate=2021-03-16|publisher=treaties.un.org|language=en}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
各缔约国考虑到《[[核能领域中第三方责任巴黎公约|核能领域中第三方责任的巴黎公约]]》及其1964年补充议定书，和《[[关于核损害民事责任的维也纳公约|关于核损害民事责任的维也纳公约]]》的相关规定；希望确保海上核材料运输过程中引起的[[核事故|核事故]]所造成的损害仅由核装置经营人负责，达成协议，制订该公约。<ref>{{Cite web|title=1971年海上核材料运输民事责任公约|url=http://www.caea.gov.cn/n6759295/n6759298/c6781997/content.html|accessdate=2021-03-16|work=|publisher=www.caea.gov.cn|language=zh-hans}}</ref>

== 内容 ==
公约主要规定如果核设施经营人根据巴黎公约或维也纳公约对事故造成的损害负责，则该损害的其他责任方可免除责任。<ref name=":0" />

